      },
      {
        "segment": "It would seem to me that, on the average, this planet would be very, very high on the list if we just took the overall amount of these problems.",
        "start_offset": 154,
        "end_offset": 298,
        "start": 23.201,
        "end": 37.661
      },
      {
        "segment": "Am I, is my feeling correct in this assumption?",
